{"tid":1647543,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"你地超成功嘅活動，係大買日！兼解鎖新活動模式！","createTime":"2019-10-11T19:48:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T13:41:17.000Z","uid":280192,"like":288,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":80,"replies":[{"pid":"51f2a6055da984d01b760309f8171116142f3e2f","tid":1647543,"uid":280192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T19:48:52.000Z","msg":"10月10大買認真成功wo, 我自己係小店老闆，雖然唔係做飲食，都感到呢條戰線係強烈風起。<br />\n<br />\n黃店排隊出曬街，旁邊d中立或藍店老闆都無曬心機！另外我發現，原來唔只懲罰黃店咁簡單，當我見到有d父母著曬黑衣口罩，推BB車排隊食，條隊勁長。我發現個影響力甚至大過出去遊行。咁落去經濟生態一定轉變。而且可以長玩。<br />\n<br />\n我夠膽講，就算其他遊行方法死曬，大買日都會係堅固無比。我為左個熱狗排兩個鐘好似好浪費時間，但如果當係遊行示威來睇，成班人兩個鐘企係條街黑衫戴口罩，呢個示威效果絕對超值。而警察又好難拉人，唔通拉顧客排隊食飯呀？！呢個係零成本，和理非都玩得。<br />\n<br />\n簡單來講，來緊遊行模式，可以係&ldquo;遊行+排隊食飯&rdquo;合一，黑衣人只要有共識係自區某堆黃店附近大排長龍，就會有遊行一樣嘅效果。<br />\n<br />\n排到食唔到都無所謂，以後開活動，可以&ldquo;食飯就係示威，示威就係食飯！&rdquo;大家慢慢玩。<br />\n<br />\nP排推不到，求幫推。認同的大佬鍾意隨便抄去開新post，或做文宣，很感謝。"},{"pid":"61ca2ca4a6d66fa6ab465c242589cfcabc27f389","tid":1647543,"uid":187668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T19:51:06.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"794666a5d6d7773477fc3de5295b17de73c4eb30","tid":1647543,"uid":30688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T19:52:07.000Z","msg":"👍🏻"},{"pid":"f2543b00bcbb801fb2ad205eedc07635a0ec1151","tid":1647543,"uid":117509,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T19:52:43.000Z","msg":"雖然有去懲罰黃店<br />\n但基本上都係商場入面<br />\n今日好成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"1423d641243830209b227ddad6f10e3048b7cb1f","tid":1647543,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T19:53:45.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">全球「和尼畫」<br />\n#XinniethePooh Challenge</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1640322/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1640322/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23XinniethePooh&amp;src=typeahead_click\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsearch%3Fq%3D%2523XinniethePooh%26src%3Dtypeahead_click&d=bDN9RnBWsu2ZFehd%2BUm4uLQTYXQauqfU4Ix09hrgZFI%3D&h=9e381687\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/search?q=%23XinniethePooh&amp;src=typeahead_click</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t0UOaVn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft0UOaVn.png&h=c7fd48b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1yAhQxD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1yAhQxD.png&h=d230a326&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「和尼畫」挑戰<br />\n1.畫出你心中所想的維尼圖<br />\n2.留下你想對習維尼講嘅說話<br />\n3.放上ig、fb、twitter，tag #XinniethePooh<br />\n4.tag 1-3個你想佢一齊畫維尼嘅朋友<br />\n5.被tag嘅朋友一齊畫維尼，讓愛與維尼佔領地球，推到畀習維尼本人見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n&quot;Xinnie the Pooh&quot; Challenge<br />\n1. Draw your own &quot;Xinnie the Pooh&quot;<br />\n2. Write down what do you want to tell Chairman Xi<br />\n3. Post your work on ig, fb and twitter with tag #Xinniethepooh <br />\n4. Tag up to 3 more friends to draw together!"},{"pid":"21a16099d7433590fc8e6d919fb8deca9ababdde","tid":1647543,"uid":61161,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T19:55:05.000Z","msg":"攞正牌遊行集會示威<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2928ad5e4e4deb4267adec6139e30f0447e00b27","tid":1647543,"uid":127454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f2543b00bcbb801fb2ad205eedc07635a0ec1151","tid":1647543,"uid":117509,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T19:52:43.000Z","msg":"雖然有去懲罰黃店<br />\n但基本上都係商場入面<br />\n今日好成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T19:58:15.000Z","msg":"街鋪都好多嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c52ffbc2dac8e5f06550608d7fdd7241261b12de","tid":1647543,"uid":280192,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"quote":{"pid":"f2543b00bcbb801fb2ad205eedc07635a0ec1151","tid":1647543,"uid":117509,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T19:52:43.000Z","msg":"雖然有去懲罰黃店<br />\n但基本上都係商場入面<br />\n今日好成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T20:02:20.000Z","msg":"我係荃灣，熱狗店雪糕店茶店拉麵店，全部係附近街檔，排曬隊好有人氣。雖然排隊規模以示威計只係雛型，但潛能真係好大。<br />\n<br />\n試想成班黑衣人排排下隊，鍾意得閒叫返句光復香港，香港人加油，差佬咬我食呀？"},{"pid":"caec896a2d0db3e87f9f60ad79ff1610a532cab5","tid":1647543,"uid":47144,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T20:02:53.000Z","msg":"間唔中一次半次ok，否則淪為快樂抗爭/嘉年華抗爭"},{"pid":"5c49cd1f76f617560e13ab21e9c291bcb17b454c","tid":1647543,"uid":280192,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T20:14:58.000Z","msg":"集中懲罰一間，就會有大排隊效果，等於遊行。<br />\n<br />\n由於呢d衛星店會大賺，可以要求老闆將部分收益捐出。如果深黃，自己賺又幫到手足，都不會介意。<br />\n<br />\n成功的話，會變成&ldquo;食飯=遊行=捐錢&rdquo;模式連hit，以戰養戰，自動回血。唔洗擔心運動的消耗。"},{"pid":"ca96310942c1d108d12bdbfcd781b9824a6183cd","tid":1647543,"uid":59961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T20:51:51.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a0245f3ca67b78809300acba5e686f854604102c","tid":1647543,"uid":300559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T20:55:27.000Z","msg":"very very support!!!!!<br />\n大買黃店"},{"pid":"1b7119113b9122360ed505556241ea88913189ad","tid":1647543,"uid":275110,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T21:09:22.000Z","msg":"我覺得策略少調整 ok，感謝日不能完全取代遊行.. 香港人繼續反坑"},{"pid":"20c61a143aa723fb1aa28b883469ffa2aac5dd13","tid":1647543,"uid":109706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T21:12:20.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"3cd3139d0d78d0ad951cbd77b50209e1c6a58c93","tid":1647543,"uid":17050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T21:26:13.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"8c2d6e112ffd3065c0e1541daaadd7364fe