3e8b0b19","tid":1647543,"uid":33579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T02:11:08.000Z","msg":"好"},{"pid":"23c982133254ae7ea110aa37a0c7889a9b81a677","tid":1647543,"uid":54564,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T02:11:43.000Z","msg":"推 等班藍店羨慕<br />\n一星期一日差唔多 慢慢養成日日都係大買日"},{"pid":"9fc092f90b6bedad6894b8fc2bd0b4e859a90400","tid":1647543,"uid":324500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"51f2a6055da984d01b760309f8171116142f3e2f","tid":1647543,"uid":280192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T19:48:52.000Z","msg":"10月10大買認真成功wo, 我自己係小店老闆，雖然唔係做飲食，都感到呢條戰線係強烈風起。<br />\n<br />\n黃店排隊出曬街，旁邊d中立或藍店老闆都無曬心機！另外我發現，原來唔只懲罰黃店咁簡單，當我見到有d父母著曬黑衣口罩，推BB車排隊食，條隊勁長。我發現個影響力甚至大過出去遊行。咁落去經濟生態一定轉變。而且可以長玩。<br />\n<br />\n我夠膽講，就算其他遊行方法死曬，大買日都會係堅固無比。我為左個熱狗排兩個鐘好似好浪費時間，但如果當係遊行示威來睇，成班人兩個鐘企係條街黑衫戴口罩，呢個示威效果絕對超值。而警察又好難拉人，唔通拉顧客排隊食飯呀？！呢個係零成本，和理非都玩得。<br />\n<br />\n簡單來講，來緊遊行模式，可以係&ldquo;遊行+排隊食飯&rdquo;合一，黑衣人只要有共識係自區某堆黃店附近大排長龍，就會有遊行一樣嘅效果。<br />\n<br />\n排到食唔到都無所謂，以後開活動，可以&ldquo;食飯就係示威，示威就係食飯！&rdquo;大家慢慢玩。<br />\n<br />\nP排推不到，求幫推。認同的大佬鍾意隨便抄去開新post，或做文宣，很感謝。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T02:14:55.000Z","msg":"係好效果既行動+文宣整合! <br />\n<br />\nP牌推唔起都推!"},{"pid":"9449e8148450c5ff1b80765a101d607d8435b868","tid":1647543,"uid":63864,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T02:15:36.000Z","msg":"我係黃店老板黎<br />\n我果日生意就同平時差唔多<br />\n不過重點唔係呢度<br />\n個重點想講就算爆買黃店幫到場活動既野都唔係好多<br />\n可以既話真係希望各位留多小小力去場運動度<br />\n只要罷買藍鋪，黃鋪自自然然會好生意嫁喇"},{"pid":"7bc03de1e9bd26ef457ef0cfa2580d892e6a9b7d","tid":1647543,"uid":324500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9449e8148450c5ff1b80765a101d607d8435b868","tid":1647543,"uid":63864,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T02:15:36.000Z","msg":"我係黃店老板黎<br />\n我果日生意就同平時差唔多<br />\n不過重點唔係呢度<br />\n個重點想講就算爆買黃店幫到場活動既野都唔係好多<br />\n可以既話真係希望各位留多小小力去場運動度<br />\n只要罷買藍鋪，黃鋪自自然然會好生意嫁喇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T02:20:08.000Z","msg":"呢個文宣個效果好，生意其次，又令社區多咗一種合法抗爭模式，保護到年青人。"},{"pid":"0dbedb5ee5e2c61063316faaf456be1c36c1ce63","tid":1647543,"uid":1025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T02:29:27.000Z","msg":"成撚日話失敗撚個d 睇下就岩 由6月到宜家都話左兄弟爬山"},{"pid":"3fe3d733c5fed2ec71ccffdfe62a8f16e5bd8332","tid":1647543,"uid":280192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2022caac0b32ebe588af46a7be737e9beb33cdfe","tid":1647543,"uid":281909,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T23:27:32.000Z","msg":"每個星期<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">所有人</span></span></span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">揀一區</span></strong></span>進行大懲罰！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同時搞埋<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">手足感謝祭</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />學生<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">出人</span></span></span>去懲罰啲<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">小黃店</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n哥哥姐姐<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">出錢</span></span></span>比你哋懲罰佢哋<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇得搞？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T02:37:16.000Z","