來講，來緊遊行模式，可以係&ldquo;遊行+排隊食飯&rdquo;合一，黑衣人只要有共識係自區某堆黃店附近大排長龍，就會有遊行一樣嘅效果。<br />\n<br />\n排到食唔到都無所謂，以後開活動，可以&ldquo;食飯就係示威，示威就係食飯！&rdquo;大家慢慢玩。<br />\n<br />\nP排推不到，求幫推。認同的大佬鍾意隨便抄去開新post，或做文宣，很感謝。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T02:47:08.000Z","msg":"建立到一個黃店生態圈就可以帶嚟改變"},{"pid":"cee809d56fc72e11fe33afc1d991677757265384","tid":1647543,"uid":277873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf767d3b1ca9b941b0c334cc884beafdca624eba","tid":1647543,"uid":146454,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"caec896a2d0db3e87f9f60ad79ff1610a532cab5","tid":1647543,"uid":47144,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T20:02:53.000Z","msg":"間唔中一次半次ok，否則淪為快樂抗爭/嘉年華抗爭"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T02:10:19.000Z","msg":"支持黃店應該要變成習慣<br />\n最後個模式應該係日日都係爆買日<br />\n唔通你會叫啲手足食六日加藤屋再食一日富臨美心？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T02:49:22.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n必須結合罷食"},{"pid":"ed1992acbfded889df6c125f645bdcb7cece8109","tid":1647543,"uid":56381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T02:50:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15298b5f7f13958f791eca422e9c200f08dcd383","tid":1647543,"uid":1430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T02:52:39.000Z","msg":"和理非一定要用盡力量 支持黃店 杯葛紅店藍店"},{"pid":"bee29f465316c4c02f0cc8bd022b2ab0e1a04eb4","tid":1647543,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T02:54:10.000Z","msg":"推！！<br />\n<br />\n每星期一次大買日！！！<br />\n<br />\n可以係星期六日/平日是但一日<br />\n<br />\n集中懲罰！！<br />\n<br />\n當然平時都要幫襯"},{"pid":"705d83d1371066d1ab4913080f05c46159752f2a","tid":1647543,"uid":41957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T02:55:28.000Z","msg":"真係好勁 隔離幾間都冇咩人<br />\n中間大排長龍 老闆做到冇停手"},{"pid":"6dbf00dd950aca0c45d65d0f4f700e75943c191c","tid":1647543,"uid":276535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T02:55:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f938d4f59b4812d5f750781af0e3d627bdb77304","tid":1647543,"uid":125680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1423d641243830209b227ddad6f10e3048b7cb1f","tid":1647543,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T19:53:45.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">全球「和尼畫」<br />\n#XinniethePooh Challenge</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1640322/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1640322/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23XinniethePooh&amp;src=typeahead_click\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsearch%3Fq%3D%2523XinniethePooh%26src%3Dtypeahead_click&d=bDN9RnBWsu2ZFehd%2BUm4uLQTYXQauqfU4Ix09hrgZFI%3D&h=9e381687\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/search?q=%23XinniethePooh&amp;src=typeahead_click</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t0UOaVn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft0UOaVn.png&h=c7fd48b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1yAhQxD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1yAhQxD.png&h=d230a326&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「和尼畫」挑戰<br />\n1.畫出你心中所想的維尼圖<br />\n2.留下你想對習維尼講嘅說話<br />\n3.放上ig、fb、twitter，tag #XinniethePooh<br />\n4.tag 1-3個你想佢一齊畫維尼嘅朋友<br />\n5.被tag嘅朋友一齊畫維尼，讓愛與維尼佔領地球，推到畀習維尼本人見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n&quot;Xinnie the Pooh&quot; Challenge<br />\n1. Draw your own &quot;Xinnie the Pooh&quot;<br />\n2. Write down what do you want to tell Chairman Xi<br />\n3. Post your work on ig, fb and twitter with tag #Xinniethepooh <br />\n4. Tag up to 3 more friends to draw together!"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T02:56:11.000Z","msg":"幅教學要整英文"},{"pid":"12ff05fd7d5fd28b4d6a1f8dfbcd4c59d331a37e","tid":1647543,"uid":281516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T02:57:37.000Z","msg":"黃色經濟圈"},{"pid":"23bb0db391ba950dbeabada88dbee04972a693e6","tid":1647543,"uid":312692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T03:00:32.000Z","msg":"PUSH<br />\n10.10己經掃咗3間黃店<br />\n但我覺得要考慮埋日後情況<br />\n諗定對應方法<br />\n因為如果呢個模式長期發展<br />\n正苦肯撚定唔會坐視不理<br />\n到時日日派食環、派消防<br />\n甚至班狗同埋黑社會去踩場"},{"pid":"f8783ef7b5a7ee608ecae146529879db650848db","tid":1647543,"uid":203813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T03:01:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b45306cacb553f87ebb87b1cd7ab9e9f9eff0f7c","tid":1647543,"uid":325884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9449e8148450c5ff1b80765a101d607d8435b868","tid":1647543,"uid":63864,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T02:15:36.000Z","msg":"我係黃店老板黎<br />\n我果日生意就同平時差唔多<br />\n不過重點唔係呢度<br />\n個重點想講就算爆買黃店幫到場活動既野都唔係好多<br />\n可以既話真係希望各位留多小小力去場運動度<br />\n只要罷買藍鋪，黃鋪自自然然會好生意嫁喇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T03:03:01.000Z","msg":"講得好，平時罷買藍店已經搞到佢地吊鹽水，日日keep住幫襯黃店再每星期或者兩星期搞一日爆買黃店，睇下藍屍鋪頂得幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8d444027658bb95332b466742fd1bd5f37b4415","tid":1647543,"uid":44751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T03:03:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2114b272aa4875b70dccd5dcb469e2c048e4197f","tid":1647543,"uid":321374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T03:03:38.000Z","msg":"排隊爆買有得做<br />\n安全底風險，最岩和理非<br />\n而且比人見到一條長龍<br />\n冇幫襯冇戶口㩒錢一樣可以鳩排<br />\n藍店就只有睇住人地賺到笑<br />\n自己就拍烏蠅等收皮"},{"pid":"9405180e7d8397b349198ce8fd7a4692237eda11","tid":1647543,"uid":56248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T03:05:26.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a694aa2c35934c4e8f6586e34cec887e878df6e","tid":1647543,"uid":179120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T03:05:37.000Z","msg":"Push"},{