0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T03:18:57.000Z","msg":"手足，對港共政權打消耗戰，黃店爆買日絕對係最有效打擊，建議每星期或兩星期搞一次。但因為個經濟效果唔係即時可見，所以呢度好多人都覺得無用。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09506576c5410ae1b5a3fd40b660b1f2e81ffbd5","tid":1647543,"uid":67717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T03:19:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"990da5d91545e64287c1560111f7f63848850081","tid":1647543,"uid":162541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T03:20:01.000Z","msg":"推行動post"},{"pid":"8657535bc16fa548091c43e50393802ceb4248c3","tid":1647543,"uid":62270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T03:20:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ef84b1e9ec4ac806a05475f1cfcdccc0e85937f0","tid":1647543,"uid":269515,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f938d4f59b4812d5f750781af0e3d627bdb77304","tid":1647543,"uid":125680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1423d641243830209b227ddad6f10e3048b7cb1f","tid":1647543,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T19:53:45.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">全球「和尼畫」<br />\n#XinniethePooh Challenge</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1640322/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1640322/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23XinniethePooh&amp;src=typeahead_click\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsearch%3Fq%3D%2523XinniethePooh%26src%3Dtypeahead_click&d=bDN9RnBWsu2ZFehd%2BUm4uLQTYXQauqfU4Ix09hrgZFI%3D&h=9e381687\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/search?q=%23XinniethePooh&amp;src=typeahead_click</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t0UOaVn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft0UOaVn.png&h=c7fd48b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1yAhQxD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1yAhQxD.png&h=d230a326&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「和尼畫」挑戰<br />\n1.畫出你心中所想的維尼圖<br />\n2.留下你想對習維尼講嘅說話<br />\n3.放上ig、fb、twitter，tag #XinniethePooh<br />\n4.tag 1-3個你想佢一齊畫維尼嘅朋友<br />\n5.被tag嘅朋友一齊畫維尼，讓愛與維尼佔領地球，推到畀習維尼本人見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n&quot;Xinnie the Pooh&quot; Challenge<br />\n1. Draw your own &quot;Xinnie the Pooh&quot;<br />\n2. Write down what do you want to tell Chairman Xi<br />\n3. Post your work on ig, fb and twitter with tag #Xinniethepooh <br />\n4. Tag up to 3 more friends to draw together!"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T02:56:11.000Z","msg":"幅教學要整英文"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T03:21:15.000Z","msg":"一早有<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PRyn4gv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPRyn4gv.png&h=ee9aa502&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n兩款poster、教學全部都中英對照晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2d350359a61bbf7eebff86fdb8bbe96bc567c6f","tid":1647543,"uid":74155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"249058e36da69b4713b716ddf0a004d564c8e669","tid":1647543,"uid":326017,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T21:56:36.000Z","msg":"不嬲話呢日係成功 <br />\n係有人吹風話連登冇人PO上黎 搞到好似好少人咁<br />\n事實係有出去食黃店既都知咩事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T03:21:23.000Z","msg":"上連登 勿認真<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa0ae04dbbc247cbbcd64b654f6e79f11214c187","tid":1647543,"uid":280192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T03:22:27.000Z","msg":"宜家出維園，都未必可以安安樂樂示威兩個鐘，出入亦有風險。<br />\n<br />\n大買日=大排隊日，反而可以成堆人安安樂樂黑衣黑罩，真心抵到爛。"},{"pid":"d23e474e44ef28c2935df9b7e06078b4ad7d4f30","tid":1647543,"uid":162541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":